#!/usr/local/projects/routing/help/html_filter.pl
<h2 align=center>Help for "Shipping Address"</h2>
To use this software, you must provide your shipping address to
create your account.  On creation, or if you change your shipping address
in the administration menu, a letter will be sent to your shipping address
with confirmation instructions.
<p>Some functions will not work without a confirmed shipping address.
